<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Registration Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #3d016f;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .list {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Rhedge Studios Tech Bootcamp</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= applicantName %>,</p>

        <p>Thank you for applying to our Tech Internship Bootcamp in <%= track %>.</p>

        <p>We've successfully received your application and are excited to review your credentials. Our team will carefully evaluate your submission and get back to you within <%= reviewPeriod %> business days.</p>

        <div class="list">
            <strong>Next steps:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Your application is now in review</li>
                <li>You'll receive our decision via email</li>
                <li>If selected, you'll receive further program details</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p>If you have any questions, please contact us at rhedgestudios@gmail.com.</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br>
        Rhedge Studios Tech Bootcamp Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Rhedge Studios. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
